<inglise>A resolution concerning the grant of or refusal to grant authorisation shall be sent to the applicant for authorisation by registered post unless it is agreed with the applicant beforehand that the resolution will be delivered to the applicant in person, against a signature. </inglise>
<eesti>29. </eesti>
<inglise>29. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Panga N&otilde;ukogu otsuse alusel vormistab Pangainspektsioon krediidiasutuse tegevusloa turvap&otilde;hjal blanketile formaadis A4 ning sellel on j&auml;rgmised rekvisiidid: </eesti>
<inglise>On the basis of a resolution of the Board of the Bank of Estonia, the Banking Supervision shall issue authorisation of a credit institution in A4 format with a printed guilloche pattern background and authorisation shall contain the following requisite information: </inglise>
