<inglise>30. </inglise>
<eesti>Pangainspektsioon v&auml;ljastab tegevusloa p&auml;rast seda, kui tegevusloa taotlejad on esitanud Pangainspektsioonile kviitungi riigil&otilde;ivuseaduse (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 86, 1461; 87, 1466 ja 1467; 93, 1563; 1998, 2, 47; 4, 63; 23, 321; 36/37, 552 ja 553; 52/53, 771; 57, 859; 59, 941; 60, 951; 61, 979 ja 985; 64/65, 1004, 1005 ja 1008; 86/87, 1408; 97, 1519; 103, 1701; 108/109, 1783; 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 275; 23, 355; 24, 359 ja 360; 25, 364; 27, 380, 384, 385, 386 ja 392; 29, 400 ja 404; 30, 415) paragrahvi 183 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud riigil&otilde;ivu tasumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>The Banking Supervision shall issue authorisation after the applicants for authorisation have submitted a receipt for payment of the sate fee provided for in subsection 183 (4) of the State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 86, 1461; 87, 1466 and 1467; 93, 1563; 1998, 2, 47; 4, 63; 23, 321; 36/37, 552 and 553; 52/53, 771; 57, 859; 59, 941; 60, 951; 61, 979 and 985; 64/65, 1004, 1005 and 1008; 86/87, 1408; 97, 1519; 103, 1701; 108/109, 1783; 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 275; 23, 355; 24, 359 and 360; 25, 364; 27, 380, 384, 385, 386 and 392; 29, 400 and 404; 30, 415) to the Banking Supervision. </inglise>
